This repository uses a split license layout.

Unless a subdirectory says otherwise, the toolchain programs and the repository's top-level build/test glue are licensed under the GNU General Public License, version 3 or (at your option) any later version.

That default applies to the source in these directories:
- archiver/
- assembler/
- compiler/
- driver/
- linker/
- simulator/ (except third-party code carrying its own notice)
- test/
- the repository root Makefile and README files

The full GPL-3.0 license text is provided in COPYING.

The runtime libraries in these directories are instead licensed under the BSD 2-Clause License:
- libraries/nlib/
- libraries/nint/

See the local LICENSE files in those directories for the exact BSD-2-Clause text.

Third-party code may carry its own license notices. For example, simulator/mos6502/LICENSE.txt remains in force for that imported code.
